---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'What age is right for sleep training?',
    a: 'Most babies are ready for gentle sleep-shaping between 4 and 6 months, but supportive habits can begin from birth. During our consultation we&rsquo;ll discuss what&rsquo;s appropriate for your baby&rsquo;s age, temperament, and feeding needs.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is it safe to sleep train? Will my baby cry it out?',
    a: 'Safety is the foundation of everything I do. I use gentle, responsive methods &mdash; not cry-it-out. Every plan follows safe-sleep guidelines and respects your baby&rsquo;s emotional needs.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What exactly does a doula do?',
    a: 'A doula provides non-medical physical, emotional, and informational support before, during, and after birth. I focus on postpartum and overnight support, helping your family rest, heal, and bond in those early weeks.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How much does this cost?',
    a: 'Pricing depends on the service and the length of support you need. After a free consultation, I&rsquo;ll send you a clear quote with no hidden fees. Payment is invoiced after we talk &mdash; there&rsquo;s no upfront commitment.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How do you schedule overnight visits?',
    a: 'After your consultation, we&rsquo;ll pick nights that fit your family. You can see my current availability in the calendar below. I&rsquo;ll confirm your preferred dates by email and we&rsquo;ll go from there.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What if I need to cancel?',
    a: 'Life with a newborn is unpredictable &mdash; I know. We&rsquo;ll talk about scheduling flexibility during our consultation so you never feel locked in.',
  },
];
---

<section class="section faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Questions, answered</span>
      <h2>What families often ask.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map((item, i) => (
        <details class:list={["faq-item", "reveal", `reveal-delay-${Math.min(i + 1, 4)}`]}>
          <summary>
            <span>{item.q}</span>
            <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p set:html={item.a}></p>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    background: var(--color-blush-100);
  }

  .section-head {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    transition: border-color 0.2s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .faq-item[open] { border-color: var(--color-maroon-300); }

  .faq-item summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-maroon-900);
    list-style: none;
    transition: background 0.2s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary:hover { background: var(--color-blush-100); }
  .faq-item summary:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-maroon-500);
    outline-offset: -2px;
  }

  .chev {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--color-maroon-700);
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .faq-item[open] .chev { transform: rotate(180deg); }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    animation: fadeAnswer 0.3s var(--ease-out);
  }
  .faq-answer p { margin: 0; }

  @keyframes fadeAnswer {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-4px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
</style>
